0139ce21-b333-45b0-98f9-f79fe4ab11e7.do_description: To make the output, you have to...Repeat the middle colors in the second half of the new grid on the same rows.
0139ce21-b333-45b0-98f9-f79fe4ab11e7.grid_description: The output grid size...double the original horizontal size with the same vertical size.
0139ce21-b333-45b0-98f9-f79fe4ab11e7.see_description: In the input, you should see...a black grid with a repeating pattern from left to right.

14cc08eb-43b0-4d1f-b0e1-14fb339828c6.do_description: To make the output, you have to...repeat the same pattern of colors in the input pixels to the grid created in the output  in the same position
14cc08eb-43b0-4d1f-b0e1-14fb339828c6.grid_description: The output grid size...the length of the grid double in size but the width stays the same
14cc08eb-43b0-4d1f-b0e1-14fb339828c6.see_description: In the input, you should see...a horizontal colored line in the middle

574db8c7-0f8b-43a9-a83a-dd112209568e.do_description: To make the output, you have to...start with one color, choose a second color, and repeats those colors. You should begin with the middle row.
574db8c7-0f8b-43a9-a83a-dd112209568e.grid_description: The output grid size...is double the length of the input.
574db8c7-0f8b-43a9-a83a-dd112209568e.see_description: In the input, you should see...a repeating pattern in which pixels are alternating by color and only use only two colors.

f5772ba2-f40c-41f4-a0a1-eba877cc35e4.do_description: To make the output, you have to...you just take the red and blue and repeat them all the way across.
f5772ba2-f40c-41f4-a0a1-eba877cc35e4.grid_description: The output grid size...it is now a 5x12 box and the red >blue pattern repeats all the way across
f5772ba2-f40c-41f4-a0a1-eba877cc35e4.see_description: In the input, you should see....a 5x6 box with on rows 2 and 3 there are alternating red and light blue boxes all the way across.

fe6c052d-3658-4f5f-bd8e-458cbbb2e3a0.do_description: To make the output, you have to...continue the horizontal pattern of blocks all the way to the end.
fe6c052d-3658-4f5f-bd8e-458cbbb2e3a0.grid_description: The output grid size... should remain the same height but double the width.
fe6c052d-3658-4f5f-bd8e-458cbbb2e3a0.see_description: In the input, you should see... a black grid with a pattern of blocks going horizontally in the middle
